linz-snap (2.7.13-1) xenial; urgency=medium

  * Refactoring two pass calculation to only calculate inverse once
  * Adding option to cache inverse results for multiple snapspec runs
  * Adding CSV format output file for easier process integration
  * Tidying command line options
  * Fixing dat2site bug creating output file with -f option

 -- Chris Crook <ccrook@linz.govt.nz>  Mon, 27 Aug 2018 15:30:00 +1200

linz-snap (2.7.12-1) xenial; urgency=medium

  * Added output_csv filelist to create catalogue of files used in snap
    adjustment
  * Enhanced handling of wildcards in snap station lists
  * Enhanced add_coordinate_file command to allow adding coordinate files
    which need an epoch for coordinate conversion
  * Enhanced ignore missing stations to allow ignoring explicit stations to
    provide more targeted error reporting
  * Added station priority option to snapspec to provide better control over
    which stations get higher orders

 -- Chris Crook <ccrook@linz.govt.nz>  Fri, 24 Aug 2018 07:30:00 +1200

